Package: ukaq
Title: Access UK Air Quality Monitoring Data
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Jack", "Davison", , "jack.davison@ricardo.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0003-2653-6615"))
Description: Importer for a myriad of United Kingdom air quality data,
    including monitoring station metadata, hourly measured concentrations,
    and pre-calculated statistics.
